name: name
desc: The custom name for this beacon. This was unused until 1.14; see https://bugs.mojang.com/browse/MC-124395

name: BEACON_EFFECTS
desc: List of effects that Beacons can apply

name: secondaryPower
desc: Secondary potion effect given by this beacon.

name: primaryPower
desc: Primary potion effect given by this beacon

name: clickedSlot
desc: Used when touchscreen is enabled

name: hoveredSlot
desc: Holds the slot currently hovered

name: FLATTENABLES
desc: Map used to lookup shovel right click interactions

name: suggestions
desc: Builder to be used when creating a list of suggestions

name: lastLightningBoltUUID
desc: Stores the UUID of the most recent lightning bolt to strike

name: WANTED_ITEMS
desc: Defaults items a villager regardless of its profession can pick up.

name: FOOD_POINTS
desc: Mapping between valid food items and their respective efficiency values.

name: lastSectionPos
desc: Player section position as last updated by TicketManager, used by ChunkManager

name: ticks
desc: How long the bell has been ringing

name: resonationTicks
desc: Warmup counter until raiders are revealed by glow and particle

name: scrolling
desc: Is {@code true} if the player clicked on the scroll wheel in the GUI.

name: startIndex
desc: The index of the first recipe to display.\nThe number of recipes displayed at any time is 12 (4 recipes per row, and 3 rows). If the player scrolled down one row, this value would be 4 (representing the index of the first slot on the second row).

name: cachedPageComponents
desc: Holds a copy of the page text, split into page width lines

name: playTurnSound
desc: Determines if a sound is played when the page is turned

name: isModified
desc: Whether the book's title or contents has been modified since being opened

name: isSigning
desc: Determines if the signing screen is open

name: frameTick
desc: Update ticks since the gui was opened

name: cursorPos
desc: Note that this can be less than selectionStart if you select text right-to-left

name: selectionPos
desc: Note that this will be greater than selectionEnd if you select text right-to-left

name: lastClickTime
desc: In milliseconds

name: OUTPOST_ENEMIES
desc: List of enemies that can spawn in the Pillage Outpost.

name: dataSectionSet
desc: Section positions with blocks in them that can be affected by lighting. All neighbor sections can spread light into them.

name: toRemove
desc: Set of section positions that can be removed, because their light won't affect any blocks.

name: conditions
desc: Conditions for the loot entry to be applied.

name: weight
desc: The weight of the entry.

name: quality
desc: The quality of the entry.

name: functions
desc: Functions that are ran on the entry.

name: resultSlots
desc: The inventory slot that stores the output of the crafting recipe.

name: resultSlot
desc: The inventory slot that stores the output of the crafting recipe.

name: selectedRecipeIndex
desc: The index of the selected recipe in the GUI.

name: input
desc: The {@plainlink ItemStack} set in the input slot by the player.

name: lastSoundTime
desc: Stores the game time of the last time the player took items from the the crafting result slot. This is used to prevent the sound from being played multiple times on the same tick.

name: resultContainer
desc: The inventory that stores the output of the crafting recipe.

name: resourcePackHash
desc: Deprecated. Use resourcePackSha1 instead.

name: updatingChunkMap
desc: Chunks in memory. This should only ever be manipulated by the main thread.

name: visibleChunkMap
desc: Same as {@link #loadedChunks}, but immutable for access from other threads. This should never be mutated.

name: entitiesInLevel
desc: Chunk positions in this set have fully loaded and their TE's and entities are accessible from the world

name: modified
desc: True if changes have been made to {@link #loadedChunks} and thus a new copy of the collection has to be made into {@link #immutableLoadedChunks}.

name: startSoundPlayed
desc: Set to {@code true} when the crossbow is 20% charged.

name: midLoadSoundPlayed
desc: Set to {@code true} when the crossbow is 50% charged.

name: targetConditions
desc: This filter is applied to the Entity search. Only matching entities will be targeted.

name: lockedFlags
desc: Goals currently using a particular flag

name: requestedItems
desc: Defines items villagers of this profession can pick up and use.

name: secondaryPoi
desc: World blocks this profession interracts with.

name: toItem
desc: An ItemStack that can have potion effects written to it.

name: foodProperties
desc: Sets food information to this item

name: baseCostA
desc: The first input for this offer.

name: costB
desc: The second input for this offer.

name: result
desc: The output of this offer.

name: INVALID_CHUNK_POS
desc: Value representing an absent or invalid chunkpos

name: drops
desc: Sets loot table information

name: columnsToRetainQueuedDataFor
desc: Section column positions (section positions with Y=0) that need to be kept even if some of their sections could otherwise be removed.

name: alreadyTicked
desc: Entries from {@link #pendingTickListEntriesThisTick} that have already run this tick.

name: randValue
desc: Contains the current Linear Congruential Generator seed for block updates. Used with an A value of 3 and a C value of 0x3c6ef35f, producing a highly planar series of values ill-suited for choosing random blocks in a 16x128x16 field.

name: mob
desc: The entity that this goal belongs to

name: color
desc: The color index used to draw the blocks of this material on maps.

name: pushReaction
desc: Mobility information flag. 0 indicates that this block is normal, 1 indicates that it can't push other blocks, 2 indicates that it can't be pushed.

name: MATERIAL_COLORS
desc: Holds all the 16 colors used on maps, very similar of a pallete system.
